# AI/ML Internship – Day 2

## Overview

Day 2 focused on understanding how raw data is prepared before building machine learning models. The session introduced essential preprocessing techniques and practical data analysis using Python.

### Key Learning Areas

* Dataset loading and inspection
* Data cleaning and preprocessing
* Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)
* Encoding categorical features
* Feature engineering
* Handling imbalanced datasets

### Practical Work

Implemented Python programs to perform preprocessing tasks and prepare datasets for machine learning applications.

